{"title":"英雄雕像（二首）","authors":["陈衍强"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":9,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄雕像（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈衍强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方志敏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当搜山的敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜出了你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后又像搜山一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搜遍你清贫的全身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除了一支钢笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和一块怀表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连一个铜板也没有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支钢笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能描绘《可爱的中国》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块怀表"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能预告开国大典的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许敌人没有想错"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像你这样的官"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道真的一无所有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他们贪婪地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再次搜遍你正气的一身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于搜到你两袖里的清风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当革命胜利后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你没有的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一些人却有了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你有的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们却少得可怜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（如刘青山张子善王宝森之流）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在你还在教科书上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注视着后人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们明白了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都来之不易"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切也容易丧失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以我们懂得了两个字——珍惜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋做的事情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我热爱所有的解放军战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为战友补袜子的雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶老大娘过马路的雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东题词的雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太伟大了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也太平凡了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是炸碉堡的雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是堵机枪眼的雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋真实如一本日记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋简单如一颗螺丝钉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们学习起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却要用一生的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望不会老去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们越活越年轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为二十二岁的雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远是我们的叔叔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叔叔是一种精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你五讲四美当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你遵守三大纪律八项注意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你在拥挤的公共汽车上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为一个孕妇让座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你其实就是一个雷锋"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}